
// The code snippet uses the [set-value] slot to update the value of the [final-message] node. It employs the [strings.replace] slot to substitute the placeholder "{{confirmation_link}}" within the [final-message] node with the URL "https://example.com/confirm?id=123". The [set-value] slot ensures the modified string is assigned back to the [final-message] node.
set-value:x:@.final-message
   strings.replace:x:@.final-message
      .:{{confirmation_link}}
      .:"https://example.com/confirm?id=123"
